author: ChrisMisan
body:
#### PR description:
This PR introduces new data record for diamond-hptdc nonlinearities compensation. For more information, please refer to: https://indico.cern.ch/event/1100184/contributions/4635498/attachments/2359270/4026918/VBORSHCH_PPS_general_06122021.pdf

#### PR validation:
Data record was validated with test calibration using writer and analyzer included in the PR.
title: Calibration record for diamond-hptdc nonlinearities compensation
